                            <li>OOP, interfaces, SOLID, LINQ</li>
                            <li>ASP.NET MVC + Razor + routing</li>
                            <li>Async patterns + clean structure</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="skill-card" data-skill-card>
                    <div class="skill-media">
                        <img class="skill-media-img" src="~/img/Prularia1.png" asp-append-version="true" alt="Javascript" loading="lazy" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="skill-content">
                        <div class="skill-kicker">Frontend</div>
                        <h3 class="skill-title">JavaScript</h3>
                        <p class="skill-desc">DOM work, async flows, UI behavior, and clean modular client-side logic.</p>
                        <ul class="skill-bullets">
                            <li>HTML/CSS</li>
                            <li>DOM + events + async/await</li>
                            <li>Vite + Tailwind (and Bootstrap when needed)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="skill-card" data-skill-card>
                    <div class="skill-media">
                        <img class="skill-media-img" src="~/img/WFMHero.png" asp-append-version="true" alt="Java" loading="lazy" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="skill-content">
                        <div class="skill-kicker">Backend</div>
                        <h3 class="skill-title">Java</h3>
                        <p class="skill-desc">Built a Price aggregator. Solid OOP fundamentals, API integration, and clean structure.</p>
                        <ul class="skill-bullets">
                            <li>REST API integration</li>
                            <li>Clean OOP structure</li>
                            <li>Project-driven learning</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="skill-card" data-skill-card>
                    <div class="skill-media">
                        <img class="skill-media-img" src="~/img/Unity.png" asp-append-version="true" alt="Unity" loading="lazy" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="skill-content">
                        <div class="skill-kicker">Game Dev</div>
                        <h3 class="skill-title">Unity</h3>
                        <p class="skill-desc">Gameplay systems, performance-minded setup, and a clean data-driven approach.</p>
                        <ul class="skill-bullets">
                            <li>URP workflows</li>
                            <li>Pooling & budgets</li>
                            <li>Systems-first design</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="skill-card" data-skill-card>
                    <div class="skill-media">
                        <img class="skill-media-img" src="~/img/AdobeSuite2.png" asp-append-version="true" alt="Adobe Suite" loading="lazy" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="skill-content">
                        <div class="skill-kicker">Creative</div>
                        <h3 class="skill-title">Adobe Suite</h3>
                        <p class="skill-desc">Visual polish for branding, motion, and presentation with a modern workflow.</p>
                        <ul class="skill-bullets">
                            <li>Photoshop comps</li>
                            <li>Premiere edits</li>
                            <li>After Effects motion</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- C -->
    <section id="C" class="section block-c">
        <div class="panel-head-full">
            <span class="panel-head-full-title">Projects</span>
        </div>
        <div class="section-inner">
            <h2 class="section-title">Projects</h2>
            <p class="section-sub">Click a project to explore more!</p>

            <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6">

    <!-- Project card -->
    <button type="button"
            class="proj-card text-left rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md p-5 shadow transition"
            data-project-card
            data-project="sales-admin">
        <div class="h-44 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-black/40 border border-white/10">
            <img src="~/img/PrulariaHero.png"
                 class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                 alt="Sales Admin Portal" loading="lazy">
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4">
            <div class="text-white font-semibold text-lg">Sales Admin Portal</div>
            <div class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">Internal MVC web app for sales teams to manage clients, orders, and sales data.</div>

            <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="proj-tag">C#</span>
                <span class="proj-tag">ASP.NET MVC</span>
                <span class="proj-tag">EF Core</span>
                <span class="proj-tag">SQL</span>
                <span class="proj-tag">Scrum</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </button>

    <button type="button"
            class="proj-card text-left rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md p-5 shadow transition"
            data-project-card
            data-project="portfolio-accordion">
        <div class="h-44 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-black/40 border border-white/10">
            <img src="~/img/PortfolioThumb.png"
                 class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                 alt="Portfolio Website — Interactive Accordion UI" loading="lazy">
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4">
            <div class="text-white font-semibold text-lg">Portfolio - Interactive Accordion UI</div>
            <div class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">Hand-built from scratch (no prebuilt modules): smooth, futuristic portfolio with accordion navigation + skill gallery.</div>

            <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="proj-tag">HTML</span>
                <span class="proj-tag">Tailwind</span>
                <span class="proj-tag">JS</span>
                <span class="proj-tag">Vite</span>
                <span class="proj-tag">UX</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </button>

    <button type="button"
            class="proj-card text-left rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md p-5 shadow transition"
            data-project-card
            data-project="java-aggregator">
        <div class="h-44 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-black/40 border border-white/10">
            <img src="~/img/WFMHero.png"
                 class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                 alt="Price Aggregator & Opportunity Scanner" loading="lazy">
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4">
            <div class="text-white font-semibold text-lg">Price Aggregator & Opportunity Scanner</div>
            <div class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">Java tool aggregating marketplace data + OCR-assisted scanning to highlight demand-driven opportunities.</div>

            <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="proj-tag">Java</span>
                <span class="proj-tag">REST</span>
                <span class="proj-tag">JSON</span>
                <span class="proj-tag">OCR</span>
            </div>
        </div>
